DF-15\"> </a></td><td>vesper</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">LK-DF-16<a name=\"cs-drug-frequency-LK-DF-16\"> </a></td><td>Weekly</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">LK-DF-17<a name=\"cs-drug-frequency-LK-DF-17\"> </a></td><td>6 hourly</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">LK-DF-18<a name=\"cs-drug-frequency-LK-DF-18\"> </a></td><td>8 hourly</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">LK-DF-19<a name=\"cs-drug-frequency-LK-DF-19\"> </a></td><td>5 Times Per Day</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">LK-DF-20<a name=\"cs-drug-frequency-LK-DF-20\"> </a></td><td>Today and repeat in 14 days</td></tr></table></div>"
